overview:
96Robots is a Toronto, Ontario based Online Marketing and SEO (Search Engine Optimization) company. The company works with companies of all sizes to develop online strategy that will keep them in touch with your customers.

96Robots offers a variety of services which includes: SEO Strategies, Developing an Online Marketing Presence, CMS website design, Graphic Design, and One-on-one cutomized training of all website tools to better understand your website.

Services Include but not are not limited to:

* Organic SEO
* Site Conversion Optimization
* Graphic Design/ Branding
* Marketing Research
* Website Design (CMS)
* Blog management/Training

These are just a few of the services we offer our customers. To view the rest please feel free to visit us at http://www.96robots.com
